CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "He's a Shy Guy - While 'Bride' Gwendolyn Davis is very nonchalant about it all, 'Groom' Charles McHenry is the traditional shy fellow at the altar. The picture was snapped during a Midget Wedding at Tabernacle Baptist Church on the North Side recently.  The affair was sponsored by the Deaconess Board of the church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tom Thumb wedding with bride Gwendolyn Davis, and groom Charles McHenry, walking down aisle in Tabernacle Baptist Church
